snippet.title: Super Monkey Ball Banana Rumble – Godzilla and Hatsune Miku Reveal – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
New paid DLC for Super Monkey Ball Banana Rumble available November 26 on Nintendo Switch! Get a taste by trying out the demo today! https://ninten.do/6056WtUJg 
 
Smash through the competition as Godzilla, the mighty King of the Monsters, or party as the cheerful Virtual Singer Hatsune Miku, ready to share her love for music with the world!  Dive into the FREE 2.00 Update, packed with a new multiplayer mode, new stages, and new challenges that will keep you rolling.  
 
#SuperMonkeyBall #Godzilla #HatsuneMiku #NintendoSwitch
